                "invention-title": [
                    "Biological deodorization method",
                    "一种生物除臭方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a biological deodorization method, which adopts the following deodorization system and deodorization method: the deodorization system consists of an odor collection system, an anoxic and aerobic treatment system and a biodegradation discharge system; the deodorization method comprises the following steps: when dissolved oxygen in the anoxic tank is less than 0.5 mg/l, sending the odor collected by the odor collection system into the anoxic tank for treatment, sending air into the aerobic tank for aeration treatment, and discharging tail gas through biodegradation; when the dissolved oxygen in the anoxic tank is greater than 0.5 mg/l, odor collected by the odor collection system is treated through the anoxic tank and the aerobic tank which are connected in parallel, the aeration air amount is closed or reduced, the dissolved oxygen in the anoxic tank is controlled to be 0.2-0.5 mg/L, the dissolved oxygen in the aerobic tank is controlled to be 2-5 mg/L, and tail gas is discharged through biodegradation. According to the system, the anoxic tank and the aerobic tank can be fully utilized to perform respective or combined deodorization on odor, the treatment air volume of the biodegradation device is greatly reduced, the pollutant concentration is low, the occupied area of the system is small, the investment is saved, hydrogen sulfide in waste gas is utilized to replace a carbon source, and the operation cost is lower."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种生物除臭方法，采用以下除臭系统和除臭方法：除臭系统由臭气收集系统、缺氧和好氧处理系统和生物降解排放系统构成；除臭方法是：当缺氧池内溶解氧小于0.5mg/l时，将臭气收集系统收集的臭气送入缺氧池处理，好氧池通过送入空气曝气处理，尾气通过生物降解排放；当缺氧池内溶解氧大于0.5mg/l时，将臭气收集系统收集臭气通过并联的缺氧池和好氧池进行处理，关闭或降低曝气空气量，缺氧池溶解氧控制在0.2～0.5mg/L，好氧池溶解氧控制在2～5mg/L，尾气通过生物降解排放。本发明系统能够充分利用缺氧池及好氧池对臭气进行分别或合并除臭，生物降解装置处理风量大幅度减小，且污染物浓度低，系统占地小，投资省，利用废气中硫化氢代替碳源，运行成本更低。"
                }
            ]
